# Deployment — tv.bakeandgrill.mv

## RULE: After EVERY `git push`, ALWAYS print this exact block — no exceptions

```
─────────────────────────────────────────
 cPanel Pull & Deploy
─────────────────────────────────────────
 1. SSH into cPanel, then run:

    cd ~/tv.bakeandgrill.mv && GIT_SSH_COMMAND="ssh -i ~/.ssh/id_ed25519 -o IdentitiesOnly=yes" git pull origin main

 2. cPanel → Setup Node.js App → RESTART

 3. Verify:
    curl https://tv.bakeandgrill.mv/api/health
─────────────────────────────────────────
```

