## NEVER do these on the cPanel server
- `npm run build` — vite is not installed on the server
- `cd /home/bakegril/tv.bakeandgrill.mv` — wrong path, use `~/tv.bakeandgrill.mv`
- `git pull origin main` alone (without `GIT_SSH_COMMAND`) — will fail with "Repository not found"

